data.title: Compaq Case Study
data.meta_description: Compaq Case Study - Free download as Word Doc (.doc), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Compaq believes that technology should inspire and liberate users to focus on what matters to them, rather than limiting them with just information. Compaq's "Inspiration Technology" aims to seamlessly deliver exactly what users want on their own terms. After acquiring Digital Equipment Corporation in 1998, Compaq became the second largest computer company in the world with the expertise and resources to offer complex enterprise computing solutions across industries.
